Distribution of 
<taxonomicName box="[343,405,332,358]" class="Arachnida" family="Caponiidae" genus="Nops" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="8" pageNumber="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
